data.description:
Welcome Home to this South Effingham move-in ready home, this stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom
residence offers an unparalleled combination of comfort and style. Immaculately maintained and
thoughtfully designed, this home is perfect for families seeking a blend of modern luxury and
convenience. The kitchen has granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, & island.
Four well-appointed bedrooms provide comfortable retreats for family members or guests. The first floor
master suite features a walk-in closet and a spa-like ensuite bathroom for added privacy. Step outside to discover a big backyard, entertaining, relaxation, and play. This home is situated in a sought-after
neighborhood known for its excellent Effingham County schools. A spacious two-car garage provides
ample parking and additional storage space.
